{"id":670326225,"lang":"cpp","time":"3 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1648642857,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"71 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/670326225/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"10.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int lengthOfLongestSubstring(string s) {\n        std::unordered_set<char> charSet;\n        int left = 0, right = 0, stringLength = s.size(), result = 0;\n        \n        while(left < stringLength && right < stringLength)\n        {\n            if(charSet.find(s[right]) == charSet.end())\n            {\n                charSet.insert(s[right]);\n                right++;\n                result = std::max(result, right - left);\n            }\n            else\n            {\n                charSet.erase(s[left]);\n                left++;\n            }\n        }\n        return result;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters"}
